My Lord...

108
00:11:39,100 --> 00:11:42,720
Even if you kill me, you won't get out.

109
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:44,270
You know it.

110
00:11:44,270 --> 00:11:46,480
Not only will I not kill you,

111
00:11:47,630 --> 00:11:50,590
I can also reward you handsomely.

112
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:53,480
Help me send a letter out.

113
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:56,860
Sending a letter out is punishable by death.

114
00:11:56,860 --> 00:11:58,740
Then I'll kill you right now.

115
00:11:58,740 --> 00:11:59,740
I'll do it!

116
00:11:59,740 --> 00:12:02,410
I'll send it, I will!

117
00:12:02,410 --> 00:12:07,650
Deliver this letter to the Seal-Holding Eunuch, Eunuch Cao.

118
00:12:08,510 --> 00:12:10,940
If you fail,

119
00:12:10,940 --> 00:12:17,150
I'll surely have a way to ensure that no one in your family survives.

120
00:12:17,150 --> 00:12:19,400
Got it!

