Where is it?

135
00:13:26,740 --> 00:13:27,870
With me.

136
00:13:27,870 --> 00:13:29,140
Hand it over.

137
00:13:29,140 --> 00:13:32,330
- Well... 
 - You've got a death wish?

138
00:13:35,220 --> 00:13:38,320
Please, sir... Sir...

139
00:13:42,270 --> 00:13:44,520
A blood-written letter?

140
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:47,360
Fine. You can go. We'll deliver it to Eunuch Cao. Go.

141
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:48,510
- Get going. 
 - Sir!

142
00:13:48,510 --> 00:13:49,960
- Just go! 
 - Please forgive me.

143
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:52,750
I must deliver it myself.

144
00:13:52,750 --> 00:13:54,920
I really have no choice.

145
00:14:01,150 --> 00:14:05,000
Since it's for Eunuch Cao, we won't stop you.

146
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:06,630
Thank you, sirs.

147
00:14:06,630 --> 00:14:08,000
Move along now.

148
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:09,630
Hurry up!

149
00:14:18,570 --> 00:14:20,830
Done.

150
00:14:24,440 --> 00:14:26,600
 We were both fooled by Zang Hai. 

151
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:28,270
 He's the last of the Kuai family. 

152
00:14:28,270 --> 00:14:29,670
 Come to me immediately. 

153
00:14:29,670 --> 00:14:32,040
Just as Xiao Hai predicted.

154
